title: An Animated Luncheon ( 1900) Directed By Edwin S. Porter

sources.title: An Animated Luncheon 1900 Directed By Edwin S. Porter
sources.description: An Animated Luncheon (1900) Director: Edwin S. Porter The scene takes place in a fashionable cafe. A well dressed couple enter, and after a careful perusal of the menu, conclude on an order of boiled eggs and Welsh rarebit.
